| ProjectHermes | PR #614 (urllib3 CVE 2026-44431/44432) — reviewer mis-classified as PREEXISTING_CI_NOISE; check-runs API showed PR-introduced | 2026-05-11 ecosystem sweep, fix-up cycle |
